summary: Mod add 3 elven presets for RaceMenu.
descriptionHtml:
Mod add 3 elven presets for RaceMenu.
[i]
DarkElfPreset - works only on Dark Elf race.

WoodElfPreset - works only on Wood Elf race.

HighElfPreset - works only on High Elf race.
[/i]
[b][size=4]Presets will not work correctly without [/size][/b][b]Ethereal Elven Overhaul. 
[/b][size=3]Other mods are optional, but without them your character will not look the same as on the screenshots.
[/size]•◕‿◕•
